# [zero] Docs never feed the zainod build (no crate include_str!'s markdown),
# so doc-only changes must not invalidate the COPY layer and force a full
# dependency recompile. live-tests/ stays included: its members are part of
# the root workspace manifest, which cargo install resolves.
docs/
**/*.md


